text: Novoyaushevo () is a rural locality (a village) and the administrative center of Novoyaushevsky Selsoviet, Mechetlinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 550 as of 2010. There are 8 streets. == Geography == It is located 32 km from Bolsheustyikinskoye. == References == Category:Rural localities in Mechetlinsky District
title: Novoyaushevo
